'''Extra dynamite''' is a switch that is categorised under the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Construction|construction patches]]. It basically allows you to demolish town owned bridges, tunnels and crossroads, things that can not be done otherwise. 

In effect, this allowing drag and drop bulldozing over towns with no worry of error messages from crossroads, As in the original game, the crossroads had to have no attaching road before they could be removed. Extra dynamite allows bulldozing them.

Extra dynamite is also a good way to destroy competitors' routes if they are running town owned roads

